Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:00.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Guys! Someday, I will go to Elbaph!\NTo the village of warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:01.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:06.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord2.9\shad2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs75}{Gi-gi-giants! Gi-giants! - OG}♪ Gi-Gi-Giants! Gia-Giants! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.15,0:02:10.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord2.9\shad2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs75}♪ Elbaph-baph! Elbaph-baph! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:13.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord2.9\shad2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs75}{Everyone's huge! 'Cause they're giants! - OG}♪ Everyone's huge\N'cause they're giants! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:17.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\b1\bord2.9\shad2\fnFOT-Greco Std B Strp\fs75}♪ They're huge! They're huge!\NThey're huge! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They sure are full of energy... - OG}They sure are lively today...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm suddenly exhausted after\Neverything that's happened. - OG}Suddenly, I'm pretty worn out\Nafter all that's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Vivi. - OG}Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Could you watch\Nthis compass for me? - OG}Could you keep an eye\Non the needle for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Now you can finally...\Nreturn to Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:46.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, assuming we can make\Nit there safely, of course... - OG}That is, assuming we can\Navoid trouble along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:50.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes. I must return! - OG}Yes. It's time I returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:53.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,After all, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:56.66,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{...the only way to save the kingdom, Princess! - OG}...the only one who can\Nsave the kingdom, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:03:01.99,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{The king—your father—no longer\Nhas sway with the people now. - OG}The king—your father—no longer\Nholds sway over his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:06.29,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our only hope of stopping\Nthis uprising now - OG}Our only hope to stem\Nthe tide of rebellion is for the country
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.63,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{is for you to tell the people\Nthe truth directly! - OG}to hear the truth directly from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:12.55,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{So, no matter what, you must not die! - OG}So, no matter the cost,\Nyou must not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.55,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You must live on, even if \Nit means losing those near to you - OG}If it means you survive,\Nthen sacrifice those closest to you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{or having to betray others! - OG}or betray them to your enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.47,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It will be painful! - OG}It will be agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.35,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Princess Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:23.93,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you resolved to stay alive?{LG 03 - 26:08; Alabasta 20 - 22:52}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will return to Alabasta, alive... - OG}I will stay alive\Nand return to Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:33.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There's no need to push yourself so hard, Vivi-chan. - OG}No need to push\Nyourself so hard, Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You have me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Today's relaxing sweets.\NHow about some petit fours? - OG}Today's sweets will put you\Nright at ease. {\i1}Petit fours{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For drinks, you have\Nyour choice of coffee or tea. - OG}And to drink, would you\Nlike coffee or tea?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:45.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yours is in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Alright!\N– Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm first! - OG}{Me first! - OG}I got there first!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,2,603...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,2,604...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If only I could've cut that wax... - OG}If only I'd been able\Nto cut through that wax...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't have left anyone hanging... - OG}we would've escaped so much sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I'm gonna get stronger... - OG}I need to get stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I need to be able to cut up\Nstuff like that from any stance! - OG}{and obtain the power\Nto cut even steel! - OG}and get to where I can\Ncut through stuff like that with ease!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I think I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{go lie down... - OG}go lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No problem, Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll keep an eye on our course. - OG}I'll keep an eye on our heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, come here! This is bad! - OG}Everyone, come here! It's urgent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? What is it, Vivi? - OG}Huh? What's up, Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:58.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san has a terrible fever! - OG}Nami has a terrible fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Eh?! Nami-san does?! - OG}Say what?! Nami has a what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mr. 2 Bon Kurei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:24.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The {\i1}Swanda{\i0} is ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:29.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay, okay! You're so loud, sheesh! - OG}Okay, okay! Dial it down a notch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Honestly, now! Why do I have to do this?! - OG}Honestly! What does any of this\Nhave to do with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mr. 3 is nothing but bulky garbage!\NYou guys go toss him out! - OG}Mr. 3 is a waste of space!\N{\i1}You{\i0} guys go finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,W-We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We wouldn't stand a chance,\Neven if we ganged up on him! - OG}Even all of us together\Nwouldn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,P-Please! It's the boss' orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Un, deux, trois...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:48.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's "four" called again? - OG}What's "four" again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Zero-[/i1]chan[/i0]is[/i1]so[/i0]high-maintenance. - OG}Zero baby is so high maintenance...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:59.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is Nami{-san} gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is she, Vivi{-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's most likely the climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:07.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{One of the obstacles all sailors\Nwho enter the Grand Line run into - OG}Illness caused by abnormal weather\Nis a well-known obstacle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:09.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{is illness caused by abnormal weather. - OG}for those new to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:16.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There are countless stories of tough, notorious pirates - OG}There are countless stories\N{\q2}of the toughest, most infamous pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{suddenly dying from this. - OG}suddenly dying from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Carelessness makes even the slightest case deadly. - OG}If left untreated,\Neven the slightest chill can be fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is there anyone on this ship with\Nany medical knowledge at all? - OG}Does someone on the ship have\Nany kind of medical training?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:38.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But eating meat makes\Nsickness go away! Right, Sanji? - OG}{Eating meat makes you feel better!\NRight, Sanji? - OG}Well, she'll feel better once\Nshe eats some meat! Right, Sanji?{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:42.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can make some basic food\Nmeant for sick people, - OG}Y'know, I can think of a few meals\Nmeant to nurse sick people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:46.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but that's entirely in\N"nursing" territory. There's no guarantee\Nit'd make her better... - OG}But nursing isn't my expertise,\Nso there's no telling if it would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Besides, I normally put\N100 times more care... - OG}{\q2}Even so, I put 100 times more care...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:55.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{into Nami-san and Vivi-chan's meals than I do with yours... - OG}into Nami and Vivi's meals\Nthan I do yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:59.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I serve them fresh meat and vegetables, for balanced nutrition. - OG}{\q2}To balance their diet, I only serve them\Nfresh meat and vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And I give all the rotting stuff... - OG}And I give the rotting stuff...{Gab, CPS}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's still good, though! - OG}It tastes great, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In any case, as long as I'm this ship's cook, - OG}My point is, as long as\NI'm this ship's cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:14.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{there'll be no problems whatsoever\Nin terms of getting a balanced diet. - OG}I will always guarantee\Nyou get a balanced diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{there are different kinds\Nof meals for sick people. - OG}sick people require specific meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What are her symptoms? What does she need? - OG}What does she need,\Nand for which symptoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't make that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:27.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Then she can just eat it all! - OG}Then feed her everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:31.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's sick because she doesn't\Nhave the energy for that! - OG}Going overboard like that\Nis bound to make her sicker!{Z- "likely make her sicker" was redundant with the first part}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{40 degrees?!\NHer fever's gone up again! - OG}I-It's at 40 degrees?!\NHer fever's gone up!{Z- reworded so that the line doesn't start with "40"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There'll be doctors when we\Nget to Alabasta, right?!}There are doctors in Alabasta, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How much longer will it take, Vivi? - OG}How long till we arrive, Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't know... - OG}A week maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but one week is out of the question... - OG}but it might be too late by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is being sick {\i1}that{\i0} bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Dunno. Never been sick.\N– Dunno. Never been sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Who in the world {\i1}are{\i0} you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{40°C fevers don't happen every day! - OG}Fevers of 40 degrees\Ndon't happen every day!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:03.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This may be a life-threatening illness... - OG}Her life may very well be at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:10.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Nami's gonna die?!\N– Don't die, Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:12.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Settle down! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's find a doctor to help Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay! Just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're going to make\Nher illness even worse! - OG}You'll make her worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:20.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No. - OG}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No. - OG}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:26.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:28.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,In my desk drawer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,there's a newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:43.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No change in course...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:47.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That can't be! - OG}This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Is it about Alabasta, Vivi{-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:57.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{300,000 royal soldiers\N - defected to the Resistance... - OG}{300,000 royal soldiers just defected to the Rebellion. - OG}{\q2}My kingdom just saw 300,000 of\Nthe Royal Army defect to the Rebellion.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:03.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It was originally a cold war, - OG}It all started as a cold war
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:07.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{with 600,000 royal soldiers and\N400,000 Resistance soldiers... - OG}{\q2}with the 600,000 Royal Army soldiers\Ndeterring the 400,000 rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But now that's suddenly changed! - OG}But this changes everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The uprising in Alabasta is finally\Ngoing to get serious now... - OG}The tensions in Alabasta are\Nonly going to intensify from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That paper's from three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:19.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can't change our speed, - OG}We can only go so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so I didn't want to worry you\Nby showing you that...}I thought if you saw this\Nyou'd only worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Understand, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Things seem very bad! - OG}Things look pretty bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Whew, that got through to\Nyou more than I expected... - OG}Whew, you got the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But you need to see a doctor! - OG}But you still need to see a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:38.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm fine... That thermometer\Nmust be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nobody gets\Na temperature of 40 degrees...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's probably just\Nsunstroke or something... - OG}It's most likely sunstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:47.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We don't need a doctor.\NI'll get better on my own... - OG}{No time for doctors,\Nso I'll get better on my own. - OG}I don't need a doctor.\NI'll get better on my own.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:51.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,For now, let's head\Nstraight for Alabasta as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thanks for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You idiot/jackass.\NShe's just acting tough. - OG}{It's just a front, jackass. - Z}Don't be stupid. It's just a front.{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:10.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{At this rate, so much blood will\Nbe shed throughout the kingdom. - OG}At this rate, blood will flow\Nthrough the kingdom's streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It'll be an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:16.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I don't stop that, Alabasta will be done for! - OG}{If I don't prevent that, this will spell the end for Alabasta! - OG}If I don't prevent that,\N{\q2}the Kingdom of Alabasta will be finished.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Crocodile will take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can't just return safely! - OG}{No! It isn't enough\Nto simply get back alive! - OG}It's not enough...\Nto simply get back alive!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I need to return as quickly as possible! - OG}I must expedite my return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:30.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{If I don't make it in time, a million citizens will \Nkill themselves pointlessly! - OG}A moment wasted means a million citizens\Nwill senselessly kill each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:32.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's a million people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:36.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What an immense burden\Nyou're carrying, Vivi{-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Urgh! What were you\Nwatching all this time?! - OG}C'mon! Were you even\Npaying attention up here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Whad'ya talking about? - OG}Whad'ya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:53.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ship's been going straight. - OG}The ship's going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:55.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, straight at a right angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look at the compass! - OG}You need to watch the needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:11:01.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't need to.\NI was watching that big cloud there. - OG}That wasn't necessary.\NI was watching that big cloud there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Clouds move and change shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, my head's killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:09.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So just leave this to me and go to bed! - OG}So then leave this to me\Nand go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm here because\NI {\i1}can't{\i0} leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The air's changed... - OG}The air's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The air? It's been nice weather\Nthis whole time. - OG}The air? The weather's been\Nnice this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Never mind! Just get the others! - OG}Forget it! Just get the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Get out here, you guys!\NGot work to do! - OG}Hey! Get out here, you guys!\NWe've got work to do!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– What?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hard to feel motivated\Nwhen you're the one giving the orders. - OG}Hard to feel motivated\Nwhen it's {\i1}you{\i0} giving the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:36.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Take the seat, hoist the sails, and catch the port side wind! - OG}{Hoist the sails and catch\Nthe port side wind! - OG}Hoist the sails\Nand catch the wind aport!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's going on, Nami-san? - OG}Everything okay, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The waves are quiet,\Nand the weather's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wind... - OG}The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wind? - OG}The wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:48.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{An immense wind...\Nis coming directly this way... - OG}The wind is picking up\Nand heading directly toward us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I think. - OG}I think th–
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:55.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're hot! Yeah, you stay inside the ship! Let's go to a doctor! - OG}You're burning up! Yeah,\Nstay inside until we find a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is my normal temperature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now quit being dumb and pull the ropes! - OG}Quit being dumb and man the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:06.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san, I know you're saying\Nthat for Vivi-chan, but if you push too hard... - OG}{\q2}Nami, I get that this is\Nfor Vivi's sake, but if you overdo it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:13.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Nami.\N - I think you really should... - OG}{If you ask me, you should– - OG}C'mon, Nami! You really ought to–{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just hurry and move the ship! - OG}Just hurry it up and turn the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sheesh... - OG}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What could it be? - OG}what could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It seems a little different\Nthan a storm... - OG}This is a bit different from a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:01.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry... back to Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:05.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I have a favor to ask, everyone! - OG}{Everyone! I have a favor to ask! - OG}Everyone, I need a favor!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:11.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I know it's not my place to ask\Nthis as a passenger on your ship, - OG}As a passenger on your ship,\NI know I have no right to ask this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:15.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but my homeland is\Nin a terrible state now, - OG}but my homeland is\Non the brink of disaster.{I love your wording but she doesn't actually say "War" so I think this is a good middle ground}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so I'd like to hurry ahead! - OG}So we need to expedite our trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We can't waste even a single minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:23.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So I want this ship to head for\NAlabasta at its fastest speed! - OG}You must take me to Alabasta\Nat this ship's top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:27.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course!\NThat's what we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So let's find an island\Nwith a doctor on it right away! - OG}{That said, let's find an island\Nwith a doctor right away! - OG}So let's find an island\Nwith a doctor right away!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:40.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's cure Nami-san as quickly as\Npossible and then go to Alabasta! - OG}The sooner we cure Nami,\Nthe sooner we get to Alabasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's this ship's fastest speed, right?! - OG}That's this ship's top speed, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We can't go\Nany faster than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:52.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As their princess, you should be\Nworried about those million citizens. - OG}Shouldn't a princess be more worried\Nabout her one million citizens?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right! So we need to hurry\Nand cure Nami-san's illness! - OG}You're right! All the more reason\Nto hurry and cure Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well said, Vivi{-chan}! I've fallen\Nfor you all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:02.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You got guts. - OG}You've got spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't overexert yourself, Nami{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, Vivi... I think...\NI am kind of... in trouble... - OG}Sorry, Vivi. Y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I might be... in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami{-san}! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:20.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is that?! - OG}What the heck is that?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's a cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:26.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! That's the direction–
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the direction our ship\Nwas just headed in! - OG}That's the direction our ship\Nwas just going!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:32.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It would've been a direct hit\Nhad we kept going straight! - OG}We would've hit it head-on\Nhad we kept our original heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:42.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We just barely made it through! - OG}We just barely missed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.91,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:50.79,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Grand Line cyclones are said\Nto be impossible to predict!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.87,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Yet, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:56.25,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{She doesn't predict weather\Nbased on standard theory... - OG}She doesn't predict weather\Nbased on prevailing theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:59.34,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if she's detecting\Nthe weather with her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've never seen such a navigator before! - OG}This navigator is one of a kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:05.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's hurry, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:08.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's go find us a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Yeah!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do we do, Vivi-chan?!\NNami-san's fever won't go down! - OG}What do we do, Vivi?!\NNami's fever won't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji{-san}! Karoo! I asked you\Nto stop freaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,See any doctors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you expect him to, you idiot? - OG}You actually expect him to, moron?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:51.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, guys. Do you think\Npeople can stand on the ocean? - OG}Hey, guys. Ever heard of people\Nwho could stand on the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can{\i0} people stand on the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{C'mon, Zoro.\NWhat kind of question is that? - OG}C'mon, Zoro.\NIs this some kind of riddle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Then... what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hi. It sure is chilly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It {\i1}is{\i0} chilly today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:32.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! Chilly, chilly!\NToday's very chilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Increase buoyancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What is that?! A watermelon?! - OG}What's that?! A watermelon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why are we shaking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold steady the rudder! - OG}Steady the rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,If anything happens\Nto Nami{-san}, I'll gut you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:03.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't tell me this... is a ship?! - OG}This thing can't actually be... a ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A p-pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:30.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{W-Wow! -OG}S-So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just when we're in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:42.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did our jumbo underwater raid ship,\Nthe Bliking, surprise you?! - OG}Surprised?! It's our jumbo\Nsubmersible raid ship, the {\i1}Bliking{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Vivi-chan! You're in charge here! - OG}Vivi! Take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:52.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:08.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ship's being attacked. - OG}The ship's under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.91,0:18:21.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Well, I had figured as much\Nfrom the looks of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:27.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you really pirates?\NYou're strange. - OG}Are you really pirates?\NThis can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is it just you four? - OG}Is it just the four of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.34,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,I find it hard to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.22,Main-207-,,0,0,10,,{\q2}that a pirate group would only have four people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He even ate the knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just watching hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:52.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, no matter.\NI'll start by asking this... - OG}Well, no matter.\NFirst, a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We want to go\Nto the Kingdom of Drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:19:00.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do you happen to have\Nan eternal pose or a log pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:05.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nope. Never even heard of the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Okay, you're done, right?! So leave! - OG}Hey, if that's everything,\Nthen get outta here!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to mess with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Don't rush life like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:18.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But if you have neither, then oh well. - OG}{But maybe you have neither. - OG}So you don't have either one, oh well.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For now, I'll take your\Ntreasure and this ship. - OG}{Since I'm here, I'll take your\Ntreasure and this ship. - OG}In that case, I'll take\Nyour treasure and your ship.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:25.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But first, I'm feeling a bit hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}is{\i0} this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't eat our ship! - OG}Get your mouth off our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,The great Wapol is currently eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:41.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Damn that bastard! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Should've done that from the very start... - OG}Should've done that from the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh? We can have at 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No, wait! We can discuss this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They started it themselves... - OG}Look what they started.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The fools! They're in a hurry to die! - OG}They're fools rushing to their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:01.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gunfire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Karoo! Watch Nami{-san}!\NI'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:10.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't do anything you can't handle! - OG}Don't bite off\Nmore than you can chew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:11.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Réception!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All bark and no bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{W-Wapol, my liege! These guys are...! - OG}W-Wapol, sir! These guys are...!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you still eating it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Say, this ship doesn't taste half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fool! You're no match\Nfor the great Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Time to get eaten by the power\Nof the Munch Munch Fruit! - OG}His Munch-Munch Fruit power\Nwill eat you whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:55.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh, hey, Vivi-chan. Has something happened to Nami-san? - OG}Oh, Vivi, is everything\Nokay with Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:20:59.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:05.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a hard-to-chew person! - OG}{The person's quite chewy! - OG}This guy's hard to chew on!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:14.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}Go flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:17.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wapol-[/i1]sama[/i0]? - OG}Wapol...?{Z- still trying to keep it a secret that he's the former king of drum, so localizing this -sama will be tough.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, this is bad!\NWapol-sama was sent flying! - OG}Hey, this is really bad!\NHe sent the great Wapol flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:27.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is terrible!\NWapol-sama is unable to swim! - OG}This is a disaster!\NThe great Wapol isn't able to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:34.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{He will surely perish and drown in the sea if we don't rescue him before he sinks! - OG}He will surely drown and perish in the sea\Nif he sinks before we can retrieve him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This isn't over, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We will make you pay for this! - OG}We'll make you pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:40.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Remember us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:42.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll get you for this! - OG}You're gonna pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Please, remember us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,898)}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:01.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What was that just now? - OG}J-Just now, what {\i1}was{\i0} all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:03.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They seemed to call him Wapol, but... - OG}So, I guess his name is Wapol?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Doesn't matter. Don't worry about it. - OG}Doesn't matter. Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:09.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's just forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:20.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Have I seen him somewhere before? - OG}Where have I seen him before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:34.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Won' her fever go down\Nif we dump water on her? - OG}Will her fever go down\Nif we dump water on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You idiot! - OG}– You dumbass!\N– You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:39.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. The sun's\Nabout to set for today, Vivi{-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:41.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yes... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.21,0:22:43.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Let's drop anchor somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We can't navigate at night\Nwithout Nami-san's instructions. - OG}We can't sail at night\Nwithout Nami's navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:47.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.92,0:23:17.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Whew, it's cold... - OG}Brr, it's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.05,0:23:23.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Almost a full moon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Brr! Oh, crap, I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:41.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're up early, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.82,0:23:44.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I can't just sit around doing nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:47.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out of this jam\Nas quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:50.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:24:02.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say, doesn't this area seem\Nkind of calm and cold? - OG}Say, isn't this area\Nunusually calm and cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:05.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sudden, strange calms...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:10.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I guess that's another thing that\Nhappens in the erratic Grand Line. - OG}I guess that's another\Nerratic quirk of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's not necessarily so. - OG}That's not necessarily the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.93,0:24:12.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's probably proof\Nthat an island is nearby. - OG}This is likely proof of a nearby island.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.31,0:24:18.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sanji-san! Could you look carefully out at the horizon? - OG}Sanji, can you carefully\Nscan the horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:19.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vivi{-chan}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:23.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A winter island is nearby.\NI'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.11,0:24:24.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Winter island?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.61,0:24:24.61,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.28,0:24:30.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Climatically there are four basic\Ntypes of islands in the Grand Line. - OG}Climate-wise, the Grand Line\Nhas four basic island types:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.91,0:24:35.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Summer islands, spring islands,\Nautumn islands, and winter islands... - OG}Summer isles, spring isles,\Nautumn isles, and winter isles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.25,0:24:39.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1439)}{And each one generally\Nhas four seasons of its own. - OG}In addition, each one generally\Nhas four seasons of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:44.25,Main-207-,,0,0,5,,{when on the Grand Line, there're at least 16 seasonal levels - OG}On the Grand Line, you contend\Nwith no fewer than sixteen seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.25,0:24:49.84,Main-207-,,0,0,5,,{you must conquer from summer island\Nsummer to winter island winter. - OG}There are summer island summers\Nand even winter island winters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.97,0:24:56.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Of course, there are many exceptions\Nand unknown climates.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.18,0:24:57.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:01.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Grand Line has lots of\Ndifferent islands one after the other, - OG}The Grand Line consists\Nof strings of various islands,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.19,0:25:05.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and that's why the seas between\Nthem have such unstable weather. - OOG}and weather is adversely affected\Non the seas between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:06.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.74,0:25:12.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Which is why stable\Nweather means an island is nearby. - OG}So when the weather stabilizes,\Nyou're near an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.99,0:25:15.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah[...]! [I see it!]There it is! - OG}You're right! There it is!{arch}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.00,0:25:21.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We found an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.29,0:25:24.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,An island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.71,0:25:27.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! An island! We found an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.51,0:25:31.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Nami! Good for you!\NThere's an island! You can get better! - OG}Hey, Nami! Great news!\NIt's an island! You'll get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.55,0:25:34.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,There's an island! An island! Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.18,0:25:40.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Island! Island! Island! Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.02,0:25:42.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just go look. I got her covered. - OG}Just go look already. I'll watch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.02,0:25:42.69,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Island! Isl...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:49.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,An island!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.99,0:25:54.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{White! It's so white! It must be snow! A snow island, huh?! - OG}White! So white! Has to be snow!\NA snow island, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.28,0:25:58.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Luffy! Just so you know,\Nwe're not here to have an adventure! - OG}Hey, Luffy! Just remember,\Nthis isn't the time for adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:00.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're dropping by to find a doctor! - OG}It's a quick stop to find a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.33,0:26:02.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're leaving once\Nwe get Nami-san looked at! - OG}Once Nami's looked at, we're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.79,0:26:04.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.29,0:26:08.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Snow is so nice and white!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.67,0:26:10.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's no use. He doesn't hear me... - OG}It's no use. He's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:13.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,H-H-Hold on! Is this a good idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.18,0:26:16.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If there's snow,\Ncouldn't there be snow monsters too?! - OG}If there's snow, won't there\Nalso be snow monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.22,0:26:19.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Besides, we're not even sure\Nif people live there or not! - OG}And we don't know\Nif people live there! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.22,0:26:21.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}My chronic can't-get-on-this-island disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.98,0:26:25.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Snow! I love snow! It's white!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.73,0:26:27.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Guess I'll get us ready to land. - OG}Guess I'll prep us for landfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.53,0:26:38.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,All this snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's pure happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:43.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,This is really something.\NWhat's with those mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:47.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Say, Luffy. Aren't you cold,\Ndressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.92,0:26:50.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's minus 10 degrees right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.17,0:26:52.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's when bears\Nget ready to hibernate!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.92,0:26:54.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.30,0:26:57.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.39,0:26:59.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Took you long enough!\N– Took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.19,0:27:06.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's a waterfall of melted snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.40,0:27:08.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We may be able to stop around here. - OG}We may be able to dock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.07,0:27:12.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,So, who's going doctor hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.15,0:27:13.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, I guess people-hunting comes first... - OG}Actually, you see any people?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.07,0:27:14.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.74,0:27:15.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Me too! - OG}So am I!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.78,0:27:17.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Okay! Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.20,0:27:19.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,That's far enough, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:27.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey. I found people.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.17,0:27:30.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,But... they don't seem too friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:33.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Attention, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.76,0:27:37.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Leave this place at once! This instant! - OG}Turn around and leave\Nthis place immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.34,0:27:39.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,We came to find a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.51,0:27:41.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We have a sick person on board! - OG}There's a sick person on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.06,0:27:44.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We won't fall for that trick,\Nyou filthy pirates! - OG}That's a dirty trick,\Nyou pirate bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.52,0:27:49.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is our island!\NWe won't let any pirates land here! - OG}On our island, any and all\Npirates are barred entry!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.15,0:27:53.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Raise anchor and leave now! Or else we'll blow your whole ship up! - OG}Raise anchor and leave,\Nor we'll blow your ship to smithereens!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.03,0:27:58.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They really hate our guts.\NAnd we've just met, too... - OG}They really hate our guts.\NAnd we've only just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.32,0:27:59.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't talk back! - OG}Less talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.53,0:28:00.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,They're shooting!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.49,0:28:02.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You didn't just do that! - OG}You did {\i1}not{\i0} just do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.41,0:28:03.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Stop, Sanji-san!\N– Bastard! - OG}– No, Sanji!\N– Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.09,0:28:17.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vivi!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=23}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=30}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
